<SceneText>
  <Speakers>
    <Section>Speaker</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>スタン</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Stahn</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>こんなことになるなんて……。
俺がリオンを信じた事が間違いだったのか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>How did it turn out like this...?
Was I wrong to trust Leon?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>……いいや、まだだ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...No, I can't think that yet!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>信じるって決めたんだ。
だったら最後の最後まで
俺はリオンを信じ抜いてみせる！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I decided to believe in him. So that's exactly
what I'm gonna do, right to the very end!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>リオン、お前の本当の心を
俺に聞かせてくれ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Leon, I'll get you to tell me
what's really in your heart!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Unreferenced</Section>
